{
  "texts": [
    "This includes the use of automatic detection systems and people's ability to identify the author of a text.",
    "We conducted a within-participants study in which the author of textual stimuli was either an AI or a human.",
    "Forty-two students from the University of Canterbury were recruited for this study.",
    "Twenty-one of them were male and 20 were female, while one person declared their gender to be different.",
    "Their ages ranged from 18 to 31, with an average of 20.9 years."
  ]
}